HEADWORD: Fair-spoken
<hw>Fair"-spo`ken</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Using fair
speech, or uttered with fairness; bland; civil; courteous;
plausible.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧A marvelous <xex>fair-spoken</xex> man.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Hooker.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
